{"tid":1432956,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保護自己(衣著，科技安全，律師支援，臨場應變及被捕後)","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T15:45:42.000Z","uid":57076,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad087e04d1c70003a3554a7ac0b6b99e1212553","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">衣着篇</span></ins></span></strong><br />\n著平民衫，帶衫換<br />\nblackbloc，買面巾遮耳仔<br />\n有戴眼鏡換眼鏡<br />\n帶純色帽<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><ins>科技篇</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n用iphone，太空卡，telegram用美國電話 number<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>律師支援篇</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n被捕即大叫名同身份證，重複幾次比記者<br />\n<br />\n交底名身份證比自己親人相熟朋友，有事聯絡律師<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>交通:</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n唔好用個人八達通，可以買多張，最好用車飛<br />\n八達通可以掉到遠一遠<br />\n<br />\n走個陣可以轉2-3程車<br />\n<br />\n例如去某個站出閘，再轉巴士/小巴等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>臨場應變:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n被捕最好即除袋，除gear<br />\n唔係iphone的話<br />\n如係andriod機就唔小心跌爛 (iphone 6之後係破解唔到，被捕先關機，然後指模係無得解鎖)<br />\n然後一定要同記者講唔舒服，要求call白車，48小時內唔好離開醫院就最好，用各種理由(心口痛，見暈)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">被捕後:</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你個刻咁驚，一定唔記得密碼架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定，一定，一定唔可以解鎖，一解就攬炒，害死自己害死同路人。<br />\n<br />\n48小時係磨練你心智，個刻要記住自己初心，要保護自己同身邊既人。<br />\n<br />\n律師未黎之前，切勿簽任何文件，解鎖同意書廢紙嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我無野講<br />\n我要去醫院<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我唔會解鎖<br />\n我唔簽文件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------<br />\n轉載參考資料<br />\n<br />\n⚖ 法律支援 <br />\n▶ 電話 Telegram<br />\n星火 98190979 @Abccbbc<br />\n民陣 65499452 @CHRFLegalSupport<br />\n民權 94632945<br />\n韋智達 91677091<br />\n伍展邦 26081400 @hksup<br />\n本民前 @HKibackup<br />\n▶ Whatsapp<br />\n民陣 65499452<br />\n民權 94632945<br />\n伍展邦 56902877<br />\n<br />\n💊 醫療支援<br />\n杏林覺醒 46100186<br />\n反送中醫療支援社工隊 @sw_medicalsupport<br />\n李醫師 @sharing_ec<br />\n<br />\n⚠️ 被捕須知<br />\n① 只提供姓名，身份證號碼<br />\n② 不要提供電話，不要解鎖電話<br />\n③ 律師未到，保持緘密，不落任何口供，不簽任何文件<br />\n④ 律師收費，各項私人事務，一律唔好回答<br />\n⑤ 我要食嘢，我要飲水，我要去廁所，我要去醫院，我冇嘢講<br />\n⑥ 要求警方提供所有文件副本<br />\n⑦ 有權要求同性警員搜身，無須脫衣<br />\n⑧ 口供一定要檢查清楚，拿取副本，記低警員編號"},{"pid":"d16d926066a6517352d3cb264bdc5864c65f0eef","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1e632cf87109865bcfe6ad6424faa6c48fa640","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ec1feb9f97714f9d8cd7a0ad966e8ee8b059adb1","tid":1432956,"uid":23433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1cb0abb5f4cf3f01535ea51ca5edd4c6b2c300","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1dfc0754611304c0450b1060beea900bd3fa584a","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e4fe1e5422fd9af6d0ebf28d714145c5682e3c9f","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"34bda853caba3f129aad4ab406ed21974e6c7415","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"電腦要有密碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43163cf084defae37c8e3f19ae69b630fa6dcb1f","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"cf0f7b4e187adf67f52cca4e34b78f915da8cb63","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"15633df422b2923d095f7569d4022243f32030f9","tid":1432956,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0c681fe7aa63d074393c8fa46cca12cfe0983461","tid":1432956,"uid":56490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"去醫院都可以計48小時？"},{"pid":"9db3ae70791298449794bbc3be6f111798ff17c3","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c681fe7aa63d074393c8fa46cca12cfe0983461","tid":1432956,"uid":56490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"去醫院都可以計48小時？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"之前有篇文講"},{"pid":"a470f901db624559c0b283f70c7fc5b5429e1d95","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"轉發:<br />\nfrom a lawyer:<br />\n發夢前：<br />\n1.一定一定要遮耳仔<br />\n-入境處會睇耳仔。<br />\n2.even係地鐵都唔好除口罩<br />\n-上court時會對比posture，e.g對比你地鐵執返飛，同埋執彈既姿勢。<br />\n3.著白飯魚<br />\n-會認鞋的，鞋套會甩。<br />\n<br />\n發夢時：<br />\n依家狗採取既Tactic係放彈後衝，要知道<br />\n1.佢痴哂反光紙 其實有好多野都好模糊<br />\n2.佢衝埋黎同捉到你有時差<br />\n3.全世界blackbloc其實佢好難認<br />\n咁如果你係最最最前個排：<br />\n佢衝過黎個時(prerequisite:有煙)真係要除gear，話自己係街坊又好乜都好。咁樣有位話佢係認錯人。我知道有啲人gear好貴，但係律師費仲貴啊。(如果你唔係最前的話希望會珍惜gear啦，我主張大家gear自己帶自己攞走，但有危險既時候都需要丟低啲gear既🙏🏻)<br />\n.......<br />\n其實玩lazer係好高明一招=<br />\n不過如果可以的話有一個位一定要照，個個就係佢。個。Cam。 我相信都唔洗解釋比大家聽點解，但呢個係好重要好重要保護到手足。<br />\n........<br />\n如果咁唔好彩俾人捉到<br />\n星火✔️<br />\n韋智達❌<br />\n<br />\n醫院時：<br />\n都係老套一句，乜都唔好簽，<br />\n你要知道，點解佢要逼妳簽啲doc，就係因為你唔簽的話，佢真係冇你乎。<br />\n<br />\n狗屋時：<br />\n暴動其實難告得入，千其唔好自招認罪！<br />\n如果佢叫你簽野：唔好簽。<br />\n如果佢寮你講野：唔好講。<br />\n就算佢打嚇氹，都唔好比佢搞到你簽野講野。見過好多次就係自己唔小心講左之後即刻落Charge。反而之後上court時你就應該指證佢個時打嚇氹。<br />\n<br />\n上庭時：<br />\n唔好搵當值律師，第一堂一定要搵個好啲既，寧願比貴少少都唔好慳。之後覺得唔好再轉都冇所謂。當值律師搵到好律師既chance好微。同時唔好令到自己還押，還押後要每8日先可以申請保釋一次，仲要撞正個好官。所以，一定要出面搵個好啲既律師！<br />\n<br />\n#請幫手手動send出去"},{"pid":"b5573a010e62505b0087dbd5395d42c1fa983f1f","tid":1432956,"uid":265498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"98190979 <br />\n<br />\n成日背唔到 我寫咗喺腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572e503ac3a18316b37bc7e13999839dd14cb2eb","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"Telegram轉美國號碼<br />\n<br />\n1. Download app &quot;second phone&quot;<br />\n2. second phone 免費試用三日，拿美國電話號碼<br />\n3. 拿左後改TG 做美國電話<br />\n4. 驗證要收SMS，Second phone 話收到但我收唔到，tg驗證倒數去到0會打你美國電話用英文讀驗證碼比你，抄低<br />\n5. 用黎入tg<br />\n6. 記得要取消訂閱否則三日後會收錢"},{"pid":"d47bbc3573f96806824b53f39030c5a319900b85","tid":1432956,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5573a010e62505b0087dbd5395d42c1fa983f1f","tid":1432956,"uid":265498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"98190979 <br />\n<br />\n成日背唔到 我寫咗喺腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d21dc328a5d2e675f099619096be8a57334a6f","tid":1432956,"uid":305510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"有冇人知道，被捕人家屬有冇咩做倒"}]}